# Local .terraform directories
**/.terraform/*

# .tfstate files
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*

# Local files for keeping track of what to do next
AGENTS.md
SPEC.md
docs/BUG.md
docs/progress.md

# Generated prod inventory (contains real IPs — never commit)
inventory-prod.ini

# Terraform variable overrides (may contain secrets)
terraform.tfvars

# Keys
*.key
*.pub
*.pem
*.crt
dev-jwt.pub\ndev-jwt.jwks
